## ğŸ“˜ API Endpoints Summary

Below is a high-level summary of the 200+ endpoints designed for this backend system:

| Category | Description | Example Endpoint |
|-----------|--------------|------------------|
| ğŸŸ© **Auth** | Register, Login, Logout, Forgot Password | `/api/v1/auth/register` |
| ğŸŸ© **Users** | Manage user profiles & roles | `/api/v1/users/{id}` |
| ğŸŸ© **Products** | CRUD for products, categories & brands | `/api/v1/products` |
| ğŸŸ© **Orders** | Create & manage customer orders | `/api/v1/orders/{orderId}` |
| ğŸŸ© **Payments** | Integrate with payment providers | `/api/v1/payments/checkout` |
| ğŸŸ© **Cart** | Add/remove items in user cart | `/api/v1/cart/add` |
| ğŸŸ© **Wishlist** | Manage user wishlist | `/api/v1/wishlist` |
| ğŸŸ© **Reviews** | Product reviews and ratings | `/api/v1/reviews` |
| ğŸŸ© **Analytics** | Dashboard metrics for sales & products | `/api/v1/analytics/sales` |
| ğŸŸ© **Admin** | Manage users, inventory & reports | `/api/v1/admin/users` |

